1986;;Blue City;;American;;Michelle Manning;;Judd Nelson, Ally Sheedy, Scott Wilson, David Caruso;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blue_City_(film);;Returning to the small Florida town where he grew up, Billy Turner learns that his father has been killed. With little help from the police, Billy will take matters into his own hands and go up against a ruthless local mob in a desperate search to find the killer.